## Course Overview

This course teaches Kubernetes from the perspective of an **application developer**, not a cluster administrator. You'll learn the resources that directly affect your code — Pods, Deployments, Services, ConfigMaps, and Secrets — with practical YAML examples you can copy into your projects.

**Prerequisites:** Basic Docker knowledge (building images, running containers). No Kubernetes experience needed.

